I suggest that you play on Rallos. The bard experience on a blue server is alright...but it's too easy to fall into the boring typical group track until your 40s. 

With Rallos, you'll be at a dissadvantage, but you would be with any class. At least you'll be able to run away as a bard, and your equipment matters less than with many other classes.

Rallos will be frustrating, but I think you'd enjoy the independence from the norm. I'm of the opinion that blue server characters are all the same until late in their careers.

